{"tid":2064928,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【青山派斬人黨】涉6.12觀塘持刀傷人 前民建聯社區幹事還押小欖","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:07:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"85261e0c035430cae4e2660e4b64bfc4ea740a18","tid":2064928,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/涉-612-觀塘持刀傷人-前民建聯社區幹事還押小欖-042112690.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B6%89-612-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E5%89%8D%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%B0%8F%E6%AC%96-042112690.html&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8tArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=b94e38c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/涉-612-觀塘持刀傷人-前民建聯社區幹事還押小欖-042112690.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XyNjW_XsDvW4PRctEgR3rg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/64c91df0-aebf-11ea-beef-d199437dbc2d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXyNjW_XsDvW4PRctEgR3rg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F64c91df0-aebf-11ea-beef-d199437dbc2d&h=2735c47e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在上周五(12日)晚上於觀塘涉嫌持刀傷人的民建聯前社區幹事鄺星宇，被警方落案控以一項傷人罪、一項襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪、以及一項管有第一部毒藥罪。他今早(15日)由警車押解往觀塘裁判法院提堂。他暫時毋須答辯，控方指被告過往曾接受精神科治療，現有自毀傾向，並反對讓他擔保。裁判官遂把被告還押小欖精神病治療中心至6月29日，以待索取被告的精神科醫生報告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方透露被告罹患嚴重抑鬱病，有自殺和自殘傾向，亦曾向父母表示有輕生念頭。而被告於案發前，曾到過精神科中心。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，報稱地產經紀、27歲的被告鄺星宇於今年6月12日，在觀塘同仁街臨時公共小巴總站襲擊馮文傑，以及非法和惡意傷害馬富善。另被告被控於同日在觀塘警署接見室3號，管有毒藥表第一部所列的毒藥。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，上周五晚約9時，有人於觀塘同仁街一個小巴站聚集，期間被告懷疑與人因政見問題爭執，並以一把長約19厘米的生果刀襲擊一名姓馮的40歲男子，一名姓馬的21歲男子企圖制止，兩人皆手部受傷。姓馮傷者拒絕送院，而姓馬傷者當時亦清醒，被送往聯合醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方之後接報到場，在被告身上檢獲一個刀盒及兩粒半懷疑第一部毒藥，並在地上檢獲一把生果刀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n2_qwAv5aleTQpmziFs78w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/7f36b620-aebf-11ea-b943-c28e3c006c2b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fn2_qwAv5aleTQpmziFs78w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F7f36b620-aebf-11ea-b943-c28e3c006c2b&h=428f07f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28ff3d8d3d5abe161b6d5c140b6b6a5712532118","tid":2064928,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"青山派分裂！<br />\n<br />\n依家出現咗：<br />\n(1) 青山派陳云根流<br />\n(2) 青山派民建聯流<br />\n<br />\n兩個流派, 爭奪緊<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">青山派正朔</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12c59ec4ae4d93780fbe7c1ce4c2b52092c59d0","tid":2064928,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"精神病最後無事"}]}